This paper is about text summarization, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Within cs.CL, the paper could also fit into subcategories such as Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL) since these fields are often used in NLP tasks.
